FastAPI Interview Questions and Answers

1. What is FastAPI?
---> FastAPI is a modern, high-performance web framework for building APIs with Python 3.7+ based on standard Python type hints.

Key Features:
  Fast: Very high performance (comparable to Node.js and Go), thanks to Starlette and Pydantic.
  Automatic Docs: Generates interactive API documentation automatically using Swagger UI and ReDoc.
  Type Safety: Uses Python type hints to validate, serialize, and document requests/responses.
  Asynchronous Support: Built on asyncio, supports both async and await.
  Validation: Built-in data validation using Pydantic models.
  Dependency Injection: Powerful, clean DI system for shared resources like DB connections, auth, etc.

